'''Sugawara Shrine''' (菅原神社) is the name of a {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社|12=draft|12=draft}} dedicated to {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|Sugawara no Michizane|12=draft|12=draft}} as its enshrined deity.
== Tōhoku Region == * {{ill|Matsudate Sugawara Shrine|ja|松舘菅原神社|12=draft|12=draft}} - Hachiman, Kazuno City, Akita Prefecture.
== Kantō Region == * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Saitama)|ja|菅原神社 (さいたま市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Minuma Ward, Saitama City, Saitama Prefecture. * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Setagaya)|ja|菅原神社 (世田谷区)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Setagaya Ward, Tokyo. * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Itabashi)|ja|菅原神社 (板橋区)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Itabashi Ward, Tokyo. * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Machida)|ja|菅原神社 (町田市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Honmachida, Machida City, Tokyo. * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Odawara)|ja|菅原神社 (小田原市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Kōzu, Odawara City, Kanagawa Prefecture.
== Chūbu Region == * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Iga)|ja|菅原神社 (伊賀市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Ueno Higashimachi, Iga City, Mie Prefecture.
== Kinki Region == * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Osaka)|ja|菅原神社 (大阪市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Kamikuratsukuri, Hirano Ward, Osaka City, Osaka Prefecture. * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Sakai)|ja|菅原神社 (堺市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Ebisunochō, Sakai Ward, Sakai City, Osaka Prefecture. * {{ill|Sanga Sugawara Shrine|ja|三箇菅原神社|12=draft|12=draft}} - Sanga, Daitō City, Osaka Prefecture. * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Nara Higashikujō)|ja|菅原神社 (奈良市東九条町)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Higashikujōchō, Nara City, Nara Prefecture.
== Chūgoku Region == * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Yanai)|ja|菅原神社 (柳井市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Yanai City, Yamaguchi Prefecture. Also known as {{ill|Yanai Tenmangū|ja|柳井天満宮|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Kyūshū Region == * {{ill|Hagiwara Sugawara Shrine|ja|萩原菅原神社|12=draft|12=draft}} - Hagiwara Town, Yatsushiro City, Kumamoto Prefecture. * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Kitakyushu Tobata)|ja|菅原神社 (北九州市戸畑区)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Sugawara, Tobata Ward, Kitakyushu City, Fukuoka Prefecture. * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Kitakyushu Kokura Kita)|ja|菅原神社 (北九州市小倉北区)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Kofunaba Town, Kokura Kita Ward, Kitakyushu City, Fukuoka Prefecture. * {{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Satsumasendai Tōgō Fujikawa)|ja|菅原神社 (薩摩川内市東郷町藤川)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Fujikawa, Tōgō Town, Satsumasendai City, Kagoshima Prefecture. * {{ill|Arahira Tenjin|ja|荒平天神|12=draft|12=draft}} - Tenjin Town, Kanoya City, Kagoshima Prefecture. Officially named "Sugawara Shrine." == See Also == * {{ill|Tenmangū|ja|天満宮|12=draft|12=draft}}
